<section class="text-intro"><h1>About us</h1><p class="lead">
    Anjo Cleaning delivers premium cleaning and dependable property care in Madeira — powered by German standards, clear routines, and genuine island commitment.
  </p></section>
<section class="text-flow"><h2>Where German precision meets Madeira</h2><p>Anjo Cleaning is built on a personal journey: from Germany to Madeira — a place that quickly became home.</p><p>We bring what owners and hosts need most: reliability, punctuality, and an uncompromising eye for detail. Locally, we add hands-on experience and direct, transparent communication.</p></section>
<section class="text-flow"><h2>Our philosophy: the best of two worlds</h2><ul class="sectionList">
<li><strong>German thoroughness:</strong> structured workflows, checklists, and consistent final inspections — for results you can see and feel.</li>
<li><strong>Island care:</strong> respect for your property, furnishings, and surroundings — we treat every home as if it were our own.</li>
<li><strong>True reliability:</strong> clear agreements, on-time delivery, fast feedback — so you stay in control at all times.</li>
</ul></section>
<section class="text-flow"><h2>Why “Anjo”?</h2><p>“Anjo” means angel — and that’s how we see our role: a calm, dependable hand in the background that keeps your property maintained, presentable, and guest-ready — whether it’s a holiday home, private residence, or office space.</p><div aria-label="Founder quote" class="quote">
<p>“My love for Madeira drives me to make this island a little more beautiful — room by room, with precision and heart.”</p>
<div class="sig">Florian Engelmann, CEO</div>
</div></section>
<section class="text-flow"><h2>Your partner in Madeira — even from afar</h2><p>Whether you live in Madeira or manage your property remotely, Anjo Cleaning is the partner that delivers premium quality, takes responsibility, and works with values you can trust.</p><p>
    Learn more about our <a data-local-link="" href="/en/landing/cleaning-for-al/">Cleaning for Alojamento Local in Madeira</a> and <a class="cta-link" href="/en/contact/">get in touch directly</a> about your property in Madeira.
  </p><p>
    Anjo Cleaning Unipessoal Lda is a cleaning company based on Madeira — specialised in holiday rentals, Airbnb and Alojamento Local (AL).
    Our focus: reliable turnover cleaning, deep cleaning, and a consistently guest-ready presentation.
  </p></section>
